Product Name: Ammae Ragi Powder - Sprouted & Roasted, 400 g
Product Description: Ammae Ragi Powder has the goodness of ragi which is known for its numerous health benefits and is a highly nutritious cereal loaded with calcium, proteins, iron and other minerals. This instant drink is a convenient way of being instantly energizing as it is rich in fiber and contains very less unsaturated fat that makes it perfect for weight loss. Ragi is a rare cereal that does not need to be polished, therefore, can be consumed in its purest form with all its goodness intact.
Manufacturer: P.k Anand, Sri Kalyani Trading Company, Plotno -p-/15/1, Road no -6, Hyderabad-East(Telangana), 500076
Usage: 1. Pour a glass (200ml) of plain water in a container.2. Add 3 teaspoons of Ammae Ragi powder to the same.3. Mix the powder thoroughly without any lumps until it gets dissolved. 4. Place the container with the mix on the stove and keep the flame on low.5. Stir the mix continuously to avoid sticking to the pan.6. Cook it for 2 to 3 minutes and pour hot milk to the mix and stir well. 8. Add sugar to taste and Ragi malt is ready to drink.

Boost is one of Indias leading Malt-based foods, fortified with a combination of micro-nutrients that are known to be essential for oxygen utilization of the body and energy metabolism. Product Name: Desi Utthana Desi Utthana diabetea-herbal-tea 100 g, 100 g
Product Description: Diabetea is made with a combination of Camellia Sinensis and the herb Gymnema Sylvestre, a woody, climbing plant, whose leaves have been used in the treatment of diabetes for over 2000 years by Indian physicians. It protects the pancreas by controlling the secretion of insulin.
Manufacturer: Asian Tea Enterprises, 12/155 Ketti Post, The Nilgiris, Tamil Nadu

Add a 3/4th teaspoonful of diabetea to a cup of boiling water.
Brew for a few minutes.
Strain into a cup and serve.
Lime can be added to taste.
Avoid milk.

Product Name: ENSURE DIABETES CARE Diabetic Care Formula - Specialised Nutrition For Diabetes Management,, 1 kg Box
Product Description: Ensure Diabetes Care is scientifically formulated with a slow-release energy system (unique carbohydrate blend including modified maltodextrin) to help optimise glycemic response. Add 6 Scoops of Ensure Diabetes Care powder in 200 ml water.
Stir until dissolved and enjoy

Product Name: Horlicks Women's Plus - Caramel, 400 g Jar
Product Description:
Bones form the structural framework of the human body. Up until the age of 30, bone formation is faster than bone loss, which causes the skeleton to grow both in size and density, resulting in an overall increase in bone mass. After the age of 30, bone mineral density may start to decrease. Unfortunately, there are no visible signs of weak bones. They often go unnoticed over many years, with no symptoms or discomfort until a bone breaks. To maintain strong bones, you dont just need an adequate intake of Calcium, but also Vitamin D for Calcium absorption and Vitamin K2 for binding Calcium to bones, daily.
Remember, Vitamin K2 is not commonly found in the Indian diet, and Vitamin D is not even available in your daily diet. Horlicks Womens Plus is a bone nutrition specialist powered with CALSEAL formula. It provides 100% RDA^ of Calcium, Vitamin D & Vitamin K2 requirements. NIH Osteoporosis and related bone diseases national resource center (https://www.bones.nih.gov/health-info/bone/bone-basics).
Ref: Malhotra N and Mithal A. Osteoporosis in Indians. Indian J med res 127, March 2008, pp 263-268. Unique combination of Vitamin K2, Calcium and Vitamin D to support bone health. In 2 serves (60 g) as per ICMR 2010 Guidelines on Women. Added sugar refers to Sucrose. 'Contains Naturally Occurring Sugars'. Horlicks Womens Plus is a nourishing beverage to be consumed as a part of regular diet.
Manufacturer: Hindustan Unilever Limited,Unilever House, B. D. Sawant Marg, Chakala, Andheri (E), Mumbai - 400 099.
Usage:
Take 3 heaped teaspoonfuls (30 gm). 
Add hot milk (200ml) while stirring to remove lumps. 
Add a little sugar if required

Product Name: Pee Safe Disposable Underarm Sweat Pads - In Pair, Folded, Straight, No Stains/Odour, 7 pcs
Product Description: Is your excessive sweating a turn-off? Do you shy away from raising hands with full confidence in public? Stinky armpits do put you in some really awkward situations. Using a deodorizer can only curb the stinky smell to some extent. However, a permanent solution for excessive sweat is too difficult to find? Not anymore, Pee Safes Disposable Underarm Sweat Pads are here to take all your sweat woos away. The disposable underarm sweat pads not only absorb the sweat and stinky odour from your armpits but also prevent the cloth from stinking, staining and colour bleeding. The sweat pads are made up of the finest material to provide all day long comfort. Due to its breathable and deodorizing nature, it keeps you dry and fresh all day long. All you need to do is, peel off the adhesive strips and stick the pad, inside the cloth in the underarm area. The pads are invisible from the outside as they are made up of fine material. These folded sweat pads are 125mm long and 120mm wide, providing optimal coverage over your sweaty armpits. The sweat pads work best with cotton clothes, however, can stick on all kinds of materials.
Manufacturer: Rainbow Fame Industrial Limited, Email: sales@rainbowfame.cn
Usage:
Remove the adhesive peel-off strips.
Sticks pad to the inside of clothing over the underarm seam.
No more stains or bad odour.

Product Name: Protinex Mama - Health & Nutritional Drink Mix For Pregnant & Breastfeeding Mothers, With High Protein & DHA, Chocolate Flavour, 250 g Tin
Product Description: During pregnancy and for the first 6 months after birth, a baby completely relies on mother for the fulfillment of his bodys nutrient requirements. Hence, a mother needs to have the proper and sufficient amount of nutrients throughout this period. Protinex Mama is a nutritional drink with high protein, made especially for pregnant and breastfeeding mothers. It helps meet the increased nutritional needs of pregnant woman so that she stays nourished, and baby grows healthy. Fortified with DHA, that helps in the proper brain development of baby. Also, enriched with folic acid that is known vital for the growth of brain and spinal cord. With 23 essential vitamins and minerals, Protinex Mama provides a sufficient dose of macro and micronutrients to the pregnant mother filling her with vitality and energy. Nutrition Now, Health Forever!

Mama Protinex contains 11 Immunonutrients that support immunity: Protein, vitamin A, vitamin C, vitamin E, vitamin D, vitamin B6, vitamin B12, folate, iron, zinc, selenium
Nutrients that contribute to normal function of immune system
Nutrition and Health Claims  European Commission, 2016.
Usage:
Add 2-3 heaped tablespoons (25g) of Protinex Mama Chocolate Flavour.
Take a mug (200ml) of lukewarm or cold milk.
Add sugar if desired.
Stir well before drinking.
